Clickjacking (UI redressing)

https://portswigger.net/web-security/clickjacking
https://portswigger.net/burp/documentation/desktop/tools/clickbandit



How to construct a basic clickjacking attack
	Basic clickjacking with CSRF token protection
		Target Website can iframed. so use payload - "Clickjarking_Payloads"



Clickjacking with prefilled form input
	Clickjacking with form input data prefilled from a URL parameter
		Target website can be iframed. so use payload - "Clickjarking_Payloads" with iframe url parameter which change email. like - "<iframe src="$url?email=hacker@attacker-website.com"></iframe>".





Frame busting scripts
	Clickjacking with a frame buster script
		Target website can be iframed. so use payload - "Clickjarking_Payloads" with iframe parameter which bypass frame buster script protection against Clickjarking. iframe parameter should be like this - "<iframe id="victim_website" src="https://victim-website.com" sandbox="allow-forms"></iframe>"





Combining clickjacking with a DOM XSS attack
	Exploiting clickjacking vulnerability to trigger DOM-based XSS
		Target Website can be iframed. so use payload - "Clickjarking_Payloads" with iframe parameter which contains XSS.




Multistep clickjacking
	Multistep clickjacking
		Target Website can be iframed. so use payloads - "Clickjarking_Payloads" with two or more "Decoy Website" buttom to conduct successful multiple actions.





	
